snippet.textDisplay: The memorable 7th dungeon from LA. Having to go through all the different floors while carrying that big ball so you can take down the pillars on each level. To be honest, I consider this one of the best dungeons in the whole Zelda series. Not only that but while I've always considered this my favorite 2D Zelda, it might even be my favorite one overall.
